    <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold">Albemarle Mesh</h1>
    <p>Albemarle Mesh is a community project design to setup a strong Meshtastic backbone in Albemarle County to facility emergancy communication during an event that has caused other methods of communication to fail. This project is currently under very active development.</p>

